  "category": "post-processing",
  "description": "Cinematic post-processing with multi-scale Gaussian bloom pyramid, anamorphic highlight streaks, and superellipse vignette. Features ACES tone mapping, split-tone shadows, film grain, and depth-driven haze. Bass boosts bloom threshold and mouse shifts vignette center.",
